{"tid":869124,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港廁所唔乾淨","createTime":"2018-10-20T06:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T07:16:01.000Z","uid":187109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f75e754a06f4da7a6821b83fedce7c497286b593","tid":869124,"uid":187109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T06:07:02.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜經過會展，有個大陸人急屎樣咁過嚟問我<br />\n大陸狗：香港有沒有踎廁<br />\n我：香港邊有踎廁架<br />\n大陸狗：怎麼辦，沒有踎廁<br />\n佢果陣個樣就嚟瀨屎咁<br />\n我：唔使諗啦，香港度度都係得坐廁<br />\n大陸狗：坐廁不乾淨<br />\n我：咪玩啦 大陸啲廁所咪仲撚唔乾淨<br />\n <br />\n香港廁所話晒都有消毒 定期有人入去清<br />\n屌你大陸啲廁所十年都冇人清一次 仲有屎漬 好意思講香港唔乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我懷疑佢地坐廁都照踎上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d7aa47594b3bc8171a98d1771d192e2f6211d5","tid":869124,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T06:14:45.000Z","msg":"屎坑雞"},{"pid":"13c5573b4a20f58c431e6ed3a5c591d06cc57fa4","tid":869124,"uid":158585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T06:21:37.000Z","msg":"叫佢求其入個地盤 用膠廁"},{"pid":"3776c559b7a9b82045687bfc7d6f7b2f237df504","tid":869124,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T07:08:52.000Z","msg":"公廁坐廁真係唔敢坐"},{"pid":"5846815364210edd9198a1ec8010efcf1f17cf27","tid":869124,"uid":198952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"03前勁污穢，之後好番，依家都接受到"}]}